cs213.photoAlbum.model

Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs213.photoAlbum.model.Tag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Tag>

    public class Tag
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Tag>, java.io.Serializable
    A Tag Class is a combination of tag type and tag value. This objects is held by a photo. A tag describes details about the photo like location, and people in the photo. A tag can be of any type and value.
    Author:
    Andrii Hlyvko
